@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us | Galaxxy Shopping Store</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #002244;
    color: #333;
}

header {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2em 0;
}

header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 3em;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
}

header h2 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.5em;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
}

section {
    padding: 3em 2em;
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 1200px;
    background-color: white;
    margin-bottom: 2em;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}

section h3 {
    border-bottom: 3px solid #333;
    padding-bottom: 0.5em;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
    font-size: 2em;
    color: #555;
}

section p {
    font-size: 1.2em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
}

section img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    margin-top: 1em;
    border-radius: 8px;
}

footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5em 0;
    font-size: 1em;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 2em;
}

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <h2>Welcome to Galaxxy Shopping Store</h2>
    </header>

    <section id="introduction">
        <h3>Introduction</h3>
        <p>At Galaxxy Shopping Store, we believe that fashion is an expression of individuality and style. Our store offers a wide range of fashion products, from trendy outfits to timeless classics, ensuring that every customer finds something that reflects their personality. Our mission is to bring the latest fashion trends to our customers with a commitment to quality and affordability.</p>
        <img src="~/media/images/pexels-mart-production-7679682.jpg" alt="Galaxxy Shopping Store">

    </section>

    <section id="history">
        <h3>Our History</h3>
        <p>Founded in [Year], Galaxxy Shopping Store started as a small boutique with a passion for fashion. Over the years, we have grown into a well-known name in the fashion industry, thanks to our dedication to customer satisfaction and our ability to stay ahead of fashion trends. Our journey has been one of innovation, creativity, and a relentless pursuit of excellence.</p>
        <img src="~/media/images/history.jpg" alt="Store History">
    </section>

    <section id="founder">
        <h3>Founder: Maheen Munir</h3>
        <p>Maheen Munir, the visionary behind Galaxxy Shopping Store, has always had a deep passion for fashion. Her entrepreneurial spirit and commitment to quality have been the driving forces behind the store's success. Under her leadership, Galaxxy has become synonymous with style, elegance, and innovation in the fashion world.</p>
        <img src="~/media/images/pexels-mart-production-7679863.jpg" alt="Maheen Munir">
    </section>

    <section id="market-value">
        <h3>Market Value</h3>
        <p>Galaxxy Shopping Store stands out in the fashion market for its unique blend of style, quality, and affordability. We have carved a niche for ourselves by consistently delivering high-quality products that cater to the diverse needs of our customers. Our market value is reflected in our loyal customer base and our reputation as a trendsetter in the industry.</p>
        <img src="~/media/images/image1.jpg" alt="Market Value">
    </section>

    <section id="fashion-industry">
        <h3>Impact on the Fashion Industry</h3>
        <p>Galaxxy Shopping Store is not just a retailer; we are a trendsetter. We play a significant role in shaping the fashion landscape by introducing new trends and styles that resonate with our audience. Our commitment to sustainability and ethical fashion practices has also set us apart as a responsible player in the industry.</p>
        <img src="~/media/images/pexels-rachel-claire-5864245.jpg" alt="Fashion Industry Impact">
    </section>

    <section id="customer-experience">
        <h3>What We Provide to Our Customers</h3>
        <p>At Galaxxy Shopping Store, we provide more than just clothing; we offer an experience. Our carefully curated collections are designed to meet the diverse tastes and preferences of our customers. From casual wear to formal attire, our products are crafted with attention to detail, ensuring that our customers always feel confident and stylish.</p>
        <img src="~/media/images/market.jpg" alt="Customer Experience">
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Galaxxy Shopping Store. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
